WEBVTT

00:03:29.054 --> 00:03:32.140
na zaidi watu wanavyosaidiana, kufundisha

00:03:32.164 --> 00:03:33.317
wengine na kushauriana,

00:03:33.341 --> 00:03:36.118
ndivyo huboresha mashirika katika kila kipimo:

00:03:36.142 --> 00:03:38.973
faida, kuridhisha wateja, kuvutia
wafanyakazi -

00:03:38.997 --> 00:03:40.842
hata hupunguza gharama za uendeshaji.

00:03:41.407 --> 00:03:42.407
Hivyo watoaji hutumia muda mwingi

00:03:42.407 --> 00:03:44.299
kusaidia wengine

00:03:44.299 --> 00:03:45.506
na kuboresha timu,

00:03:45.530 --> 00:03:48.006
kwa bahati mbaya, wanajikuta kwenye hasara.

00:03:48.030 --> 00:03:49.698
Nataka kuzungumzia namna ya

00:03:49.722 --> 00:03:53.043
kujenga utamaduni ambapo watoaji wanafanikiwa.

00:03:53.564 --> 00:03:56.584
Hivyo nilijiuliza kama watoaji sio 
watekelezaji bora,

00:03:56.608 --> 00:03:58.436
wapi ni watekelezaji bora?

00:03:59.438 --> 00:04:02.088
Nitanza na habari njema:
siyo wapokeaji.